action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
description:
It was discovered that PCL incorrectly handled certain malformed files.
If a user or automated system were tricked into opening a specially crafted
file, an attacker could possibly exploit this to cause a denial of service.
isummary: PCL could be made to crash if it received specially crafted input.
